"Tareeq" is an innovative technological system that aims to transform the chaos of the public transportation sector into an integrated, smart system. "Tareeq" serves as a bridge connecting passengers and vehicles and a centralized management system, providing a smooth and organized transportation experience.

This system provides accurate and real-time information on microbus routes and schedules, helping users save time and effort and reach their destinations with ease. "Tareeq" is an important step toward building a more efficient and smarter city.
